name: Tiny Police Line - Sticky Tape
description:
STICK EM UP! 

The Tiny Police are on the case...be it securing that tricky parcel, customising a new Moleskin sketch book, or meticulously <del>stealing</del>, borrowing every bit of stationery from your friend's desk. Fire up your imagination and get sticking. 

Perfect for someone who's a Tiny bit Columbo.

This is one complete roll of awesome sticky tape, made on quality vinyl tape... like those leading brands, only more fun. No iPhones, chocolates, tissues, other props or imagination included.

http://www.aintrocketscience.co.uk

name: Better Late Than Never Poster. As Seen On TV
description: Top notch A1 Poster as seen on Channel 4's excellent IT Crowd! Thanks to our friends at Talkback Thames, quite a few of our designs where chosen to dress the set of the latest series. Just in case you've never seen it, the IT Crowd is an Award-winning comedy from writer Graham Linehan. Banished from the ivory towers of Reynholm Industries, the IT crowd lurk below ground, avoiding work and social contact in equal measure. It is available (certainly in the UK) to watch online at 4od. No TVs, chocolates, tissues or other props included. The full set can be seen Zazzle
